<p><a href="#sdfootnote95anc" name="sdfootnote95sym">95</a>This tendency resonates with philosophies of object-oriented ontology and new materialism. The members of World of Matter creatively engaged with the writing of theorists such as Michel Serres, Bruno Latour, Graham Harman, and Karen Barad, and connect to climate-justice activists such as Vandana Shiva and formations such as the Landless Workers’ Movements in Brazil. For more see Arns, <em>World of Matter</em>.</p>
